text: Ernest Vicogne (17 January 1888 - 25 May 1975) was a French gymnast. He competed in the men's team event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1888 births Category:1975 deaths Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Reims
